{
  "text": "To test LDL receptor gene expression in vivo, the adenovirus Adv/ RSV-rbLDLR was infused into the portal circulation of Watanabe rabbits. Hepatocytes were isolated from these rabbits 3 d postinfusion, and the binding and uptake of '\"I-labeled human LDL were measured as described above. Hepatocytes from rabbits infused with a recombinant adenovirus bearing the human a,-antitrypsin gene (Adv/RSV-hAAT) [CITATION_1] were used as a negative control.",
